(i) 'Aadhaar number' shall have the meaning assigned to it in clause (a) of section
2 of the Aadhaar (Targeted Delivery of Financial and Other Subsidies, Benefits and
Services) Act, 2016 (18 of 2016);

• pension or family pension payment orders (PPOs) issued to retired employees
by Government Departments or Public Sector Undertakings, if they contain the
address;

(b) deposit, withdrawal, exchange or transfer of funds in whatever currency,
whether in cash or by cheque, payment order or other instruments or by electronic or
other non-physical means;

(b) necessary for extraordinary expenses, provided that such determination has been
notified by the MEA to the UNSC or its Committee, and has been approved by the
UNSC or its Committee;

(ii) the CNO has determined that the payment is not directly or indirectly received by
an individual or entity in the designated list under this Order;
